## Key Gotchas

- вқҢ Breaking IDMEEditor interface вҶ’ All dependent apps break
- вқҢ Missing [AddinAttribute] on datasources вҶ’ Won't be discovered
- вқҢ Not implementing IDataSource fully вҶ’ Runtime errors
- вқҢ Throwing exceptions вҶ’ Use IErrorsInfo instead
- вқҢ Not setting ErrorObject вҶ’ Callers don't know what failed
- вқҢ Blocking on async вҶ’ Use .ConfigureAwait(false)
- вқҢ Not initializing Entities list вҶ’ Metadata unavailable
- вқҢ Hard-coding SQL вҶ’ Use IDataSourceHelper instead
- вқҢ Not using partial classes вҶ’ DMEEditor becomes unwieldy

## Where to Ask Questions

- Interface/contract issues: Review IDMEEditor.cs, IDataSource.cs
- Configuration: Check ConfigEditor.cs and JSON file formats
- Datasource lifecycle: Look at GetDataSource, CreateNewDataSourceConnection
- Assembly discovery: Check AssemblyHandler.Core.cs and [AddinAttribute]
- Helper generation: Check IDataSourceHelper implementations and factory

## Data-Management Integration Map

These layers are not independent вҖ” they hand off to each other. When you change one, expect to touch the next.

| Layer | Owns | Hands off to (вҶ’) | Receives from (вҶҗ) |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Setup Framework** (`SetUp/SetupWizard.cs`) | First-run wizard: driver вҶ’ connection вҶ’ schema вҶ’ seed | migration (schema), configuration (persist connection), etl (optional initial load) | вҖ” |
| **Migration Manager** (`Editor/Migration/MigrationManager.cs`) | Plan, dry-run, execute, rollback, rollout governance | configuration (record history) | setup (initial schema), forms (drift reports) |
| **Schema Manager** (`Editor/Schema/SchemaManager.cs`) | Cross-datasource preflight + sync-draft production + drift/snapshot/structure resolution | beepsync (executing the draft), migration (initial schema + drift) | etl (preflight), importing (delegated shims) |
| **Configuration** (`ConfigUtil/ConfigEditor.cs`) | Persisted JSON state: connections, queries, mappings, drivers, migration history | вҖ” | setup, migration, etl, forms, uow (all read/write through it) |
| **ETL Engine** (`Editor/ETL/Engine/PipelineEngine.cs`) | Cross-datasource data movement, scheduling, observability | вҖ” | setup (initial load), configuration (mappings), workflow (invocation) |
| **Workflow Engine** (`Editor/ETL/Engine/Workflow/WorkFlowEngine.cs`) | Multi-step business processes | etl, forms (human tasks) | any layer that wants process-level orchestration |
| **Forms Manager** (`Editor/Forms/FormsManager.cs`) | Master-detail UI lifecycle and mode transitions | uow (every save) | setup (post-init runtime), etl (display output) |
| **UnitOfWork** (`Editor/UOW/UnitofWork.cs`) | Transactional CRUD for app code | вҖ” | forms (UI saves), etl (transactional sinks) |

